Important information

Safety Information:

Store in cool and dry place

Directions:

Start off with a primer and then apply the foundation for an easily blendable experience. Finish off with the compact and play with your eyes with colors, kajal, liner, and mascara. While you’re applying your eyeshadow, place a cotton pad under your eyes to avoid messing up with your base makeup. Apply the lip & cheek tint as a blush and then use the highlighter to highlight cheek bones, nose and corner of eyes. Complete your look with your favorite lipstick!

Product description

Iba Must Have Complete Makeup Box for Women (Fair) l with 11 Essential Products l Waterproof l Bridal Makeup l Full Face Makeup | 100% Vegan & Cruelty Free

Introducing the Iba Must Have Complete Makeup Box for Women a comprehensive collection of essential makeup products that cater to all your beauty needs. This makeup box contains a carefully curated selection of high-quality cosmetics to help you achieve a flawless and radiant look. All the products in the Iba Must Have Complete Makeup Box are formulated with gentle and skin-friendly ingredients. They are free from harmful chemicals making them suitable for all skin types including sensitive skin. With the Iba Must Have Complete Makeup Box you have everything you need to create stunning makeup looks for any occasion.
